description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City and Potomac! On Salt Lake, the women go snow fishing, Mary poots, and Meredith's sunglasses defy gravity. Over on Potomac, the women meet for an elegant driveway party to celebrate a podcast launch.


RHOP: 35:10ish
